snippet.title: J-Stars Victory Vs+ - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
J-Stars Victory Vs+ is available NOW on the PlayStation 4, PlayStation 3, and PlayStation Vita!

Over 50 characters from 32 different series come together for the ultimate showdown!
